01:22:21,825 --> 01:22:25,194
- One
- The way you hold my hand

655
01:22:25,410 --> 01:22:28,115
- Two
- Your laughing eyes

656
01:22:28,332 --> 01:22:31,594
- Three
- The way you understand

657
01:22:31,812 --> 01:22:34,837
- Four
