832
01:50:22,787 --> 01:50:29,289
That upon seeing you again

833
01:50:29,503 --> 01:50:33,775
I'd be crying

834
01:50:34,512 --> 01:50:37,633
I thought

835
01:50:37,854 --> 01:50:40,950
That I was over you

836
01:50:41,158 --> 01:50:48,111
