886
02:03:56,225 --> 02:03:59,487
- Everyone, please!
- Can Diane stay?

887
02:03:59,704 --> 02:04:03,250
Yeah, sure, Diane can stay.
Hank, let Diane stay!

888
02:04:03,462 --> 02:04:05,265
Diane!

889
02:04:10,664 --> 02:04:14,032
Now, when she starts to cry,
