A surprise.

913
02:09:29,575 --> 02:09:31,415
Shortcut.

914
02:09:33,993 --> 02:09:36,497
Come on, sweetheart.

915
02:09:41,823 --> 02:09:43,767
It's beautiful.

916
02:09:43,980 --> 02:09:46,305
A secret path.

917
02:10:54,017 --> 02:10:56,201
Perfect timing.

918
02:10:56,906 --> 02:10:59,052
Welcome, Diane.

919
